{"tid":2428523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇表示：K11 Musea安全","createTime":"2021-03-01T15:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T15:48:55.000Z","uid":64694,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc03fcc068357dd45f64b98f796e07343448b94","tid":2428523,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"袁國勇：相信名潮食館感染群組由短距離空氣傳播引起<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇到K11 Musea視察後指，名潮食館的鮮風量只有申請牌照時設計的三分之一，相信出現感染群組是短距離空氣傳播引起。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇：「我們量度出來，較他們原本申請牌照鮮風量只是正常的三分一，這是很不理想。大家可以看到這幅圖，鮮風會經這些藍色喉管，輸送到這些地方，有些少輸送到這裡，但這個位置的空氣，基本上是困住，即形成了感染空間，有一個地方空氣流動非常低，這裡的食客非常易受感染。」<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇又指，另一播毒源頭可能緣於茶水間，食館地下茶水間不僅沖茶，還放置用過的食具，不排除出現交叉感染。<br />\n<br />\n他又指K11 Musea公用地方、廁所及通風系統良好，認為商場是安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=425759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425759&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1yKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=1bbf7398\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425759&h=a5b15d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=425759</a>"},{"pid":"7a762206a4ea93a4a6425881183a5df26df6fa4a","tid":2428523,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:17:29.000Z","msg":"頭先差啲打錯咗做袁國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4b10d57f78bc585cef6ee8f3222fa73535513a","tid":2428523,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"Ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe3a936f28c139bf1722306a2fa7e90c50c295d","tid":2428523,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851ae21ab99b47af93a036d28f691e3670ee8058","tid":2428523,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"所以就解釋到點解去長洲行街冇戴口罩都冇事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a097e1569bfb9db435b3421cbd62663322b7db","tid":2428523,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"得佢一個起到9up話邊到唔安全<br />\n果到唔安全炸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}